🔥 I believe we’re on the verge of one of the biggest moves in the market.




#Bitcoin is testing a critical RSI trendline on the weekly chart — and historically, breaking through it has triggered massive price rallies. If $BTC can confidently close above $92,000, I think it would confirm the bullish trend and ignite a real altseason wave.




🚀 Why I’m watching this level closely:

Weekly RSI breakout = powerful signal for $BTC

$92K aligns with the 20-week moving average, a key indicator in past cycles

This could completely shift market sentiment from bearish to bullish




📈 I’m also seeing a strong correlation with global liquidity:

Every time global M2 money supply starts to rise, altcoins follow shortly after. We’re right in that historical time window where breakouts tend to begin.




💥 I’m tracking this setup closely. If #BTC holds above $92K, altcoins could absolutely explode.
